{
  "keyword": "CRTDTAARA",
  "description": "Create Data Area (CRTDTAARA)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "DTAARA",
      "description": "Data area",
      "help": "Data area (DTAARA)\n\nSpecifies the name and library of the data area being created.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Data area\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": true,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*CURLIB",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "*CURLIB"
        },
        {
          "name": "DTAARA",
          "description": "Data area",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": true,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "MYDTAARA"
        }
      ],
      "positional": 1,
      "basic": true,
      "objectKind": "dataArea"
    },
    {
      "name": "TYPE",
      "description": "Type",
      "help": "Type (TYPE)\n\nSpecifies the type of value contained in the data area being created. The type can contain a character value, a decimal value, or a logical value (1 or 0), or a distributed data management (DDM) data area can be created.\n\nThis is a required parameter.",
      "inputType": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "attributes": {
        "restricted": true,
        "characterSet": "upper"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "*DEC",
          "value": "*DEC"
        },
        {
          "label": "*CHAR",
          "value": "*CHAR"
        },
        {
          "label": "*LGL",
          "value": "*LGL"
        },
        {
          "label": "*DDM",
          "value": "*DDM"
        }
      ],
      "positional": 2,
      "basic": true,
      "valueMap": {
        "*CHAR": "C",
        "*DDM": "R",
        "*DEC": "D",
        "*LGL": "L"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "LEN",
      "description": "Length",
      "help": "Length (LEN)\n\nSpecifies the length of the data area being created. If it is a decimal data area, the number of decimal digits to the right of the decimal point can be optionally specified. The type of data area determines the maximum length that a value in that area can have and the default length that is assumed when a length is not specified. The maximum lengths and the defaults for each of the three types are as follows:\n\nNote: For character types, the default length is the same as the length of the initial value, if one is specified for the Initial value (VALUE) parameter.\n\nElement 1: Length\n\nElement 2: Decimal positions",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": false,
      "groupKind": "elements",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LEN",
          "description": "Length",
          "inputType": "number",
          "required": false,
          "attributes": {
            "numericOnly": true
          },
          "placeholder": "10"
        },
        {
          "name": "DEC",
          "description": "Decimal positions",
          "inputType": "number",
          "required": false,
          "attributes": {
            "numericOnly": true
          },
          "placeholder": "0"
        }
      ],
      "positional": 3,
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "TYPE",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "NE",
              "compareValue": "R"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "VALUE",
      "description": "Initial value",
      "help": "Initial value (VALUE)\n\nSpecifies the initial value that is assigned to the data area when it is created. The value must be of the type specified for the Type (TYPE) parameter of this command. If no value is specified, a character data area is initialized to blanks, a decimal data area is initialized to a value of 0, and a logical data area is initialized to 0.",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "positional": 4,
      "placeholder": "0",
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "TYPE",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "NE",
              "compareValue": "R"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "attributes": {
        "maxLength": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "RMTDTAARA",
      "description": "Remote data area",
      "help": "Remote data area (RMTDTAARA)\n\nSpecifies the name of the remote data area on the target system. The data area does not need to exist when the DDM data area is created.\n\nQualifier 1: Remote data area\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": false,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "RMTDTAARA_LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "*LIBL"
        },
        {
          "name": "RMTDTAARA",
          "description": "Remote data area",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "RMTDTAARA"
        }
      ],
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "TYPE",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "EQ",
              "compareValue": "R"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "RMTLOCNAME",
      "description": "Remote location",
      "help": "Remote location (RMTLOCNAME)\n\nSpecifies the name of the remote location that is used with this object.\n\nNote: Multiple DDM data areas can use the same remote location for the target system. The remote locations used must point to systems that are at a release of the operating system that supports remote data areas.\n\nMore information on remote locations is in the APPC Programming book, SC41-5443.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *RDB",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 8
      },
      "placeholder": "*RDB",
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "TYPE",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "EQ",
              "compareValue": "R"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "RDB",
      "description": "Relational database",
      "help": "Relational database (RDB)\n\nSpecifies the relational database entry that is used to determine the remote location information for the DDM data area.",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 18
      },
      "placeholder": "MYRDB",
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "TYPE",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "EQ",
              "compareValue": "R"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "DEV",
      "description": "APPC device description",
      "help": "APPC device description (DEV)\n\nSpecifies the name of the APPC device description on the source system that is used with this DDM data area. The device description does not need to exist when the DDM data area is created.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *LOC",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*LOC",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 10
      },
      "placeholder": "*LOC",
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "TYPE",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "EQ",
              "compareValue": "R"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "LCLLOCNAME",
      "description": "Local location",
      "help": "Local location (LCLLOCNAME)\n\nSpecifies the local location name.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *LOC, *NETATR",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*LOC",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 8
      },
